@startuml
title Sequence - SD-007: Goi y dia diem thong minh

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  DatabaseBorderColor Black
  DatabaseBackgroundColor White
}

actor "Nguoi dung" as User
boundary "Trang Goi y" as UI
control "Recommendation API\n/api/recommendations" as API
control "DeepSeek API" as AI
database "Co so du lieu" as DB

autonumber 1

User -> UI: Truy cap trang
User -> UI: Chon tieu chi (vung mien, loai hinh, ngan sach)
User -> UI: Nhan "Goi y cho toi"

UI -> UI: Tao preferences\n(regions, categories, budget)
UI -> API: POST preferences\n+ token neu dang nhap

API -> API: Validate request\nLay userId, tao sessionId
API -> DB: Query 30 dia diem dang hoat dong\nkem province, category, tags
DB --> API: Tra ve destination context

API -> API: Tao prefSummary\nva prompt goi y
API -> AI: Gui system prompt + user message
AI -> AI: Phan tich so thich\nva chon 5-8 dia diem phu hop
AI --> API: Tra ve JSON\n(id, name, reason, matchScore, summary)

API -> API: Parse ket qua AI

loop Moi dia diem duoc AI chon
  API -> DB: Query chi tiet dia diem\nkem anh chinh, category, province
  DB --> API: Tra ve destination day du
end

API -> DB: Luu recommendation log\n(userId, sessionId, preferences, results)
DB --> API: Xac nhan luu

API --> UI: Tra ve recommendations\n+ summary + total + algorithm
UI -> UI: Chuan hoa matchScore va aiReason
UI --> User: Hien thi danh sach goi y\nkem diem, ly do, anh, thong tin tom tat

User -> UI: Bam vao mot dia diem
UI --> User: Chuyen sang trang chi tiet\n/destinations/{slug}

@enduml
